description:
Rappers Stunna 4 Vegas and Mariah Lynn join the ladies of Lip Service this week. Stunna opens up about why he's so choosy when it comes to being with women, talking nasty in the bed and much more. Stunna and Mariah even roleplay as if they were trying to kick it to each other. Enjoy!
